    <constitutionalAuthorityStatementText><![CDATA[<pre>From the Congressional Record Online through the Government Publishing Office [<a href='http://www.gpo.gov'>www.gpo.gov</a>]By Mr. CARTER of Georgia:H.R. 1444.Congress has the power to enact this legislation pursuantto the following:Article I, Section 8 of the Constitution.[Page H2316]</pre>]]></constitutionalAuthorityStatementText>
